Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:07.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\NWithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:32.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:38.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.59,0:01:02.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\NWhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:25.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:28.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:33.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rioters have gathered at\NHakuto Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:35.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Kokuryo Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:37.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to your defense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:38.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rioters have gathered at\NHakuto Gate and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kokuryo Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to your defense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:46.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready you bastards--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, don't let up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:07.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it, Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…you did…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Riot away as you please\Nin Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!\NYou're not passing this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the Ryoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There're Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Halt! We're not letting you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:51.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya, that's an amazing technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this is where\Nwe part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What kind of joke is that?\NWe were going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said that your role is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:39.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we going to\Ncrush Seireitei together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:48.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or, to put it another way,\Nyou're just a means to open this gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seireiheki shuts out\Nall spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nit is impossible to destroy it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or pass through it\Nusing spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:02.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NYou were using us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying that\Nyou're of no use now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:08.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From this point on,\Nit's my tribe's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:10.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just in the way\Nif you linger around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've been tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:18.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NWe can't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:47.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The gate is open?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that device?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:30.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They call themselves Soul Reapers?\NThey're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:34.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The real battle is about to begin.\NDon't underestimate the captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told Mabashi and Yoshi\Nto create diversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:42.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You two crush each squad captain\None by one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,while Mabashi and Yoshi\Nare causing riots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:55.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our final goal is to completely\Ndestroy Seireitei. Instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They created us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and yet they tried to wipe away\Nour existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Judgment must be passed\Nupon the Seireitei for their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we need something in\Norder to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go and get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\Nthere's something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with that kind of destructive force\Nin Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:16.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the Department of Research\Nand Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon find out…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our final meeting place\Nis the Sokyoku Hill. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? If you have something\Nto say, then say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:39.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… Good luck…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:54.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo… Get ahold of yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah…you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NYou saved me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing… Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:24.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, everything's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:27.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, it'll take time for\Nthe seireiheki to be fully open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well… Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:40.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that you're injured,\Nbut could you open the gate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:44.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Of course!\NWait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:07.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right! Go quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds have opened…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:11.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying his best in spite\Nof his wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let his efforts go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:24.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:30.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki! I'm staying back!\NI have to heal Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:35.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!\NWell, what kind consideration…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurodo, go with everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:42.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:43.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm all right!\NLeave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo, you can let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue stayed back\Nbecause she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:09.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take her feelings into consideration…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:15.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's a reason\Nshe left you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lirin, how are the Spiritual Pressure\Nof the Bounts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:23.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I don't sense any right now.\NI wonder if they're hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:28.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… But they've come\Nthis far with a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They can't hide their\NSpiritual Pressure forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:36.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who can sense\Nthe Bounts the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We need your help!\NKurodo, we're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:54.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll trust Orihime and\Ngive it my all to search for the Bounts…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:55.47,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will find them…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, once his mouth opens…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:56.52,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…and crush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he just doesn’t stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.70,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.57,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:02.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Split up! Right now,\Nwe have to track the Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:03.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A hell butterfly--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen Court Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with\Nspecial order level one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,all captains are\Nurgently summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:21.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will hold a captains' meeting.\NI repeat…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen Court Guard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with\Nspecial order level one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,all captains are\Nurgently summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will hold a captains' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Continue dispatching to\Nthe assigned areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:39.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can only keep searching\Nuntil we find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When you do find them,\Ndon't approach them immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:46.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Contact other groups and wait for help!\NThat's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:47.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man! I'm not\Ngetting any hits at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep searching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… Where did Kariya go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, you're so hyped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What good is it not to be hyped\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Calm down a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why--?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:12.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My sensors don't work properly with\Nsomeone who's worked up next to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:13.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:16.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:18.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really! You run a lot more\Nroughly than Orihime. Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… You're the Punishment Force,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a Ryoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Ryoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:50.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that, I heard you guys\Nare strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You want to fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeige Dich, Ritze.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ritze, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:43.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:56.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Captain Jushiro Ukitake\Nof Squad 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping. It seems that\Nhe's not feeling well again…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:03.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… Squad 2 Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the status of\Nthe Punishment Force…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:12.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have already positioned groups\Nthroughout Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very good… A very quick response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:16.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:21.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what has the captain of\NSquad 10 done in comparison
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to the Punishment Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:28.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was the commander\Nfor the annihilation of the Ryoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that he allowed them\Nto invade Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:35.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has some nerve,\Ncalling himself a commander…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make excuses.\NIt is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. It can't be helped\Nthat they got in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to think of what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:54.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki. It seems that\Nyou fought the man called Kariya…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he's their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to reveal what\Nyou know to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can control wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, he can control reishi\Nand has a powerful regenerative ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was saying that we should\Nquestion the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the captain of Squad 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:19.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About a Quincy tool…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:30.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They were able to come here because\Nsomeone gave them a Quincy tool
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that was in the Department of Research\Nand Development…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably all a set up…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're good at ignoring\Nyour own shortcomings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Think about other peoples' \Nfeelings a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am also irritated right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I know how to\Ntake responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, where did you\Nhear about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have sharp ears…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is not the time\Nto be quarreling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:15.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nare to spread out within Seireitei…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the Ryoka when\Nthey find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:23.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is best if we deal with\Nthe Ryoka as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:29.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, from now on,\Neach squad will take their own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:35.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Squad 10 captain will be relieved\Nof his duties as temporary commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:42.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reports are to be done quickly\Nand immediately. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:47.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Mayuri, are you \Ngoing out in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:52.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I hate being made fun\Nof more than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:58.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Time was wasted on\Nthat unnecessary captains' meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think this is over, Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:06.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving you in charge!\NDo what needs to be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sense a Bount!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now it disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're not just\Nsaying things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I was positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Curse those Bounts\Nfor sneaking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guerrilla warfare is most effective
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when taking on an army\Nwith a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is pretty good…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:41.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do\Nto praise them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's hurry to the place\Nwhere you sensed them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:51.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! Turn right at that corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man! It's appearing and\Ndisappearing like an old flashlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:02.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty hyped up despite telling\Nme to calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if\NI'm the one that's hyped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. That's so selfish…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:17.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:19.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:23.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:41.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yo..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Ryoka, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:51.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the scary faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ritze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving on, Ritze!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:32.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mabashi is doing well.\NNow then, I should go as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:50.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting! It appears that group two\Nand group three have met the Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did they get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The information is complicated.\NThe result is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:57.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How irritating…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:19:59.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead of me! Gather all groups\Nat Seireitei's northern streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:07.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:07.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:29.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Group two and group three,\Ngive me your reports…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Group two reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Ryoka we apprehended\Ngot away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Group three reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We encountered a Ryoka at\NWestern Street Number Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were unable to\Napprehend him…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A level one guard position\Nhas been ordered out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What good will it do us if
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Punishment Force isn't\Nfunctioning properly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:21:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ritze… It's about time…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rearrange battle positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Groups one and two are to spread out\Nalong the western streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Groups three and four are to make\Na detour eastward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and head for the main road!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:21.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:22.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:30.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:35.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:36.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:41.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NWhat did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:16.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You always lament on\Nhow boring this town is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:20.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Searching for a place in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:25.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The melody you hum is that\Nrusty, same old song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:29.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,…Rejecting any new song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:38.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're anxious because somewhere\Nin your heart, you believe in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's you;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:48.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That pain will eventually become\Na memory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:57.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think, just feel,\Nlet your whole body tremble;
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,future is you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, it's me;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:08.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're never alone, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We should be as one;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:14.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, I don’t mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:21.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell you now\Nabout the thing called love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Komamura,\Nisn't it inconvenient
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:26.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to have your lieutenant\Nout of commission?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:30.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. It's not as\Nif Tetsuzaemon wanted to be injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:32.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei isn't doing anything right now.\NDo you want to hire him temporarily?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:32.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That would be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about what he wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:34.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are no rights for a lieutenant\Nin middle management.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:38.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woah…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:49.80,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:51.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:59.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Where are those Ryoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:03.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had any appearances lately.\NAnd now look at what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.36,0:24:07.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be burned to ashes\Nby these flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:09.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Ryoka! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:14.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I, Ikkaku Madarame, will take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:19.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot… It's hot, man…!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:27.85,On Top,Default,0000,0000,0000,,LET’S HAVE COMPASSION